snippet.title: Sonic Spinball - LifeSavers Candystand Version
snippet.description:
Believe it or not, Candystand.com once hosted their own version of Sonic Spinball (with SEGA's blessing, naturally), likely tying in with the release of SEGA Smash Pack for Game Boy Advance. It's not until just recently via an upload on Sonic Cult that the game was finally made available again in some capacity.

Compared to the other pinball titles made by Skyworks (who created these games for Candystand, Nabiscoworld, etc), Sonic Spinball has a faster ball and is a lot more animated all-around.
